metadata.name: Pioneer #1
metadata.description:
Pioneer is a project designed and dedicated to us, web3 pioneers, creators and builders of this incredible space, which unites and sometimes divides. Which makes us frustrated but sometimes happy. I imagined each of us as a solitary astronaut who, traveling in the immensity of this space, finds his place where to build his little house. Each of us, a single person, but who all together create a community. The pioneer community.

Each work was created using AI software combined in several parts so as to make images customizable.
